"Coffee Stout brewed by Sierra Nevada Brewing Co. ,with an ABV of 6.90 %  This brew pours out a dark brown color with a a nice light brown head. It has the look of like coffee.  The smell is rich with coffee and hops. You also pick up on some grain s, malts, and sweetness in the smell.  Now for the taste,it is rich with flavor. There is a lot going on in this brew. You pick up on the coffee and the hops.  Then the aftertaste, is smooth with flavor, and mild sweetness. Coffee Stout is like the best of both worlds coffee and brew.  This brew has a nice balance to it there is nothing over powering in it. The mouthfeel is rich and bold with flavor.  Over all I'm giving this brew a 4.75 out of 5. Sierra Nevada Brewing Co. did a nice job with this one.  One of the better brews I have had in a long time."
